<p class="contextTtl" id="p1" data-pid="1"><span id="page241" class="pageNum" aria-hidden="true" data-no="241" data-before-text="241"></span><strong>レッスン58</strong></p>
<h1 id="p2" data-pid="2"><strong>エホバを愛して従い続ける</strong></h1>
</header>	<div class="clearfix alternatePresentation clickable noTooltips
		">
		<div class="thumbnail">
			<img src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/2012" class="lightbox"
				 data-alt-src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/2015"
				 data-alt-type="svg"/>
		</div>
		<div class="title">印刷版</div>
	</div>
	<div class="clearfix alternatePresentation clickable noTooltips
		hidden">
		<div class="thumbnail">
			<img src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/2013" class="lightbox"
